data.description: **Brand New Roof!!** New roof scheduled to be installed. Lovely manufactured home on 4 acres with a split floor plan of 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Cozy and efficient pellet stove in the living room and a fenced dog run off the back patio. Huge 30x40 detached 3 car garage with remote opener from inside the house. The partial barn presents a fantastic opportunity for horse lovers, as it can easily be transformed into multiple horse stalls, creating an ideal equestrian setup. Electrical horse fencing will stay with the house. There are two 2500 gallon water storage tanks to haul your own water or have it delivered.
